[chara_show  name="顏可韓"  time="200"  wait="true"  storage="chara/1/IMG_7196-removebg-preview.png"  width="582"  height="1262"  left="-131"  top="30"  reflect="false"  ]
[chara_show  name="柔安"  time="200"  wait="true"  storage="chara/3/IMG_7237-removebg-preview.png"  width="579"  height="1044"  left="219"  top="137"  reflect="false"  ]
[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#
到了教室，可韓和閨蜜們一樣聊天打哈哈，完全沒有提起昨天的夢境。[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[chara_hide  name="柔安"  time="0"  wait="true"  pos_mode="true"  ]
[chara_move  name="顏可韓"  anim="true"  time="300"  effect="linear"  wait="true"  left="179"  top="30"  width="582"  height="1262"  ]
[chara_show  name="皓原"  time="200"  wait="true"  storage="chara/5/greeting_1-removebg-preview.png"  width="541"  height="1101"  left="-85"  top="91"  reflect="false"  ]
[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#皓源
「早啊！」[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#
皓源一如往常地向她們打招呼，然後跑去和其他人聊天了。[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[chara_hide_all  time="1000"  wait="true"  ]
[chara_show  name="皓原"  time="200"  wait="true"  storage="chara/5/normal_1-removebg-preview.png"  width="526"  height="1041"  left="-91"  top="128"  reflect="false"  ]
[chara_show  name="奇"  time="200"  wait="true"  storage="chara/4/consider_saying_2-removebg-preview.png"  width="546"  height="1097"  left="232"  top="127"  reflect="false"  ]
[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#皓源
「關於CPC比賽...」[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#可韓
『？！！』[p]
『那不是昨天那個男生嗎？怎麼會出現在我們班？』[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#
可韓朝皓源那邊望去，看見昨天那男生也跟著他們一起聊天，看起來很熱絡。[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#可韓
「我是不是眼花了，他和皓源很熟嗎？他是我們班的嗎？不不，如果他是，我怎麼從來沒有印象？他叫甚麼名字？？」[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[chara_hide_all  time="0"  wait="true"  ]
[chara_show  name="柔安"  time="200"  wait="true"  storage="chara/3/saying_5-removebg-preview.png"  width="520"  height="1045"  left="23"  top="151"  reflect="false"  ]
[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#柔安
「你在自言自語甚麼？你再說誰？」[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#
柔安疑惑地看向可韓。[p]
[_tb_end_text]

